22
00:03:17,180 --> 00:03:18,230
I won't disturb you two.

23
00:03:18,550 --> 00:03:19,740
I'll take my leave now.

24
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:23,700
It seems

25
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:25,390
