78
00:06:19,230 --> 00:06:20,070
Why are you here?

79
00:06:21,180 --> 00:06:22,020
I...

80
00:06:24,550 --> 00:06:25,620
I went to look for Xu.

81
00:06:26,180 --> 00:06:27,110
He went to the banquet,

82
00:06:27,550 --> 00:06:29,016
