83
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:31,060
Xu is still inside.

84
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:32,500
Go wait for him. I'm leaving.

85
00:06:41,790 --> 00:06:42,910
Why are you following me?

86
00:06:43,060 --> 00:06:44,079
