199
00:12:44,860 --> 00:12:46,460
Mr. Duan, you jest.

200
00:12:47,310 --> 00:12:48,230
I heard

201
00:12:48,230 --> 00:12:50,070
you're a regular here.

202
00:12:50,430 --> 00:12:52,590
And Luoxian, the lady of this house,

203
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:54,740
