211
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:09,830
I understand you.

212
00:13:12,470 --> 00:13:13,620
And look at my sister.

213
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:15,470
A noble lady, graceful and poised.

214
00:13:15,900 --> 00:13:17,140
Why would she mind

215
